README.md
Dockerfile.builder

# Monitoring/observability config (not needed at runtime)
monitoring

# Integration tests
integration

# Test files
**/*_test.go

# Generated framework adapter files (emitted at build time by
# adapters/adapter_v*/cmd/main.go and at customer-build time by
# cmd/build/build.sh). Source of truth lives in
# adapters/common/codegen. The pattern is module-root relative
# because cmd/embed evaluates .embedignore patterns inside each
# discovered module — only per-adapter modules have an
# adapter/adapter.go to begin with.
**/adapter/adapter.go

# Dynclient subtree (patched-BAML fork + generated dynamic-only
# client + regeneration tooling). Excluded from the server-side
# embed because the customer-build pipeline embeds repo sources
# to drive its own server codegen, and the dynclient artifacts
# are independent — they ship as a separate Go package to
# downstream consumers, not through the customer build path.
dynclient
cmd/regenerate-dynclient
